<p>President Obama believes that nobody in America should go broke because they get sick, which is why he signed the Affordable Care Actinto law in 2010.</p>
 
<p>The law gives hard-working, middle class families the security they deserve and protects every American from the worst insurance company abuses.</p>
 
<p>And now, from October through March, millions of Americans can sign up for insurance that fit their needs and their budgets at HealthCare.gov.</p>
 
