      <div id="right-rail">
      <div class="cp_tile ">  <div id="block-nodeblock-226826" class="clear-block block block-nodeblock ">
  <div class="content">  <h3>A Better Bargain</h3>
  <div class="signup-text">
  <p>Nearly five years after the start of the Great Recession, President Obama kicks off a series of speeches laying out the progress we’ve made since then and the work that’s left to do to rebuild an economy where everyone who works hard can get ahead.</p>
</div>
<p class="email-text">Get updates about future speeches and the economy</p></div>
